{"tid":2440403,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中伏！","createTime":"2021-03-10T02:29:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T05:15:26.000Z","uid":391522,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6daae5a91073736bd6a4296370f0302224217dca","tid":2440403,"uid":391522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T02:29:57.000Z","msg":"粉嶺有間韓國餐廳&mdash;梨泰院 出曬名難食<br />\n但係晚晚都仲係咁多人排隊<br />\n買外賣都要等個零鐘<br />\n而且啲員工服務態度差到爆<br />\n但係聽講佢黎緊又開分店<br />\n本身已經係大埔都有間 <br />\n不過大埔分店好少少但未至於好食<br />\n啲野飲仲要好撚貴 仲要污糟<br />\n我見過有幾個客飲熱飲都投訴杯野有蚊<br />\n個環境都好鬼污糟下 野食成日有條頭髮<br />\n真係好撚想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n難食嘅野生意額特別高 <br />\n但係好食嘅就冇咩生意甚至執曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我試過一次之後都唔想再食<br />\n唔知各位Ching有冇北區美食好介紹呢"},{"pid":"bd41d06ffd5af0efca2a7abb0cfd16937130662e","tid":2440403,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T03:40:40.000Z","msg":"係facebook見到同一篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79cddaf3df0a773f20c69505950b9e2d11fe66e2","tid":2440403,"uid":277869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd41d06ffd5af0efca2a7abb0cfd16937130662e","tid":2440403,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T03:40:40.000Z","msg":"係facebook見到同一篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T04:32:20.000Z","msg":"有無link？"},{"pid":"79c21d5a4369d868213f98b36b4ffa758d96f4d7","tid":2440403,"uid":289459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79cddaf3df0a773f20c69505950b9e2d11fe66e2","tid":2440403,"uid":277869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd41d06ffd5af0efca2a7abb